topic.title: The LAST chance of seeing Chinese on free Internet
topic.body:
Note: I lives in China.

As the title said.
Too many Chinese languages in ZeroTalk English forum makes you troubled, but it is will be gone soon.

---

China government is doing (or will do possibly):

#### Real name sign

> If you sign up an account on a website in China:
> 1. Forcibly bind phone number with real name
> 2. Forcibly bind website account with phone number
>
>
> - http://news.xinhuanet.com/tech/2017-01/03/c_1120232196.htm
> - http://www.cac.gov.cn/2015-02/04/c_1114246561.htm

#### Remove foreign TV / movie 

> - [https://www.zhihu.com/question/62353049](https://github.com/zcyzcy88/SelfColle/blob/master/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%9C%8B%E5%BE%85%202017.7.12%20AcFun%E3%80%81%E5%93%94%E5%93%A9%E5%93%94%E5%93%A9%E3%80%81%E6%96%B0%E6%B5%AA%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%A4%96%E5%9B%BD%E7%94%B5%E5%BD%B1%E3%80%81%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86%E5%89%A7%EF%BC%9F%20-%20%E7%9F%A5%E4%B9%8E.mht)

#### Take down VPN service provider

> They can technical block by GFW, also they can administrative take down provider.
> It is Illegal to provide VPN service if you are not on their whitelist.
> - https://theinitium.com/article/20170127-mainland-vpnban

#### Block Shadowsocks

> - https://www.google.com/patents/CN105281973A
> - https://docs.google.com/viewer?url=patentimages.storage.googleapis.com/pdfs/c4655bdfd3bcee64d0a3/CN105281973A.pdf

#### [possible] Install a "CleanNet" software on your device, which can monitor all your activities.

> If you don't install, connect the Internet is not allowed.
> Think it as an advance [绿坝](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Green_Dam_Youth_Escort)

#### Connect and scan your file in your smartphone.

> - http://imgur.com/a/d20Um
> - [http://tieba.baidu.com/p/5228179646](https://web.archive.org/web/20170719114840/http://tieba.baidu.com/p/5228179646)

---

**Crazy. What the FUCK.**

## I think, government will possibly cut off all Internet soon, then build a "China Intranet", just be like Xinjiang.

- https://theinitium.com/article/20170124-mainland-xjnetoff
- https://commondatastorage.googleapis.com/letscorp_archive/archives/8174
